Description:
    creates basic structure for petridish 
Example:
    bin/rails generate petri_dish:request_specimen
    will generate:
        config/initializers/petri_dish.rb if file doesn't allready exist. 
    

bin/rails generate petri_dish:query_specimen
    will generate: 
    should initialize diffent file than request_specimen
    config/initializers/petri_dish.rb
    